Detective-inspector
ALFRED NICHOLLS, K Division. I went to 9, Mermaid Court, about a quarter past 10 on the night of February 4, and went up to the rooms occupied by prisoner and deceased. There was a light in the room. I found the two rooms in a state of con
fusion; the door between the two bad apparently been forced; there were marks on it corresponding to this short poker which I produce;

